feat(moderation): Implement comprehensive content reporting system with automated analysis

This PR introduces a robust content reporting system for TimelyCapsule, featuring automated content analysis, priority management, and enhanced admin tools.

Key Features:
- Content reporting system with automated analysis
- Priority-based report management (urgent, high, normal, low)
- Intelligent content categorization
- Enhanced admin notification system

Technical Changes:
- New Models:
  - Enhanced Report model with priority and analysis fields
  - Added content analysis service for automated moderation
  - Integrated with existing notification system

- API Endpoints:
  - POST /reports - Create report with auto-analysis
  - GET /reports/my-reports - User's reports
  - GET /reports - List all reports with filtering
  - GET /reports/pending - Priority-filtered pending reports
  - PUT /reports/:id/review - Review with notification
  - DELETE /reports/:id - Remove report

- Security:
  - Authentication required for all endpoints
  - Admin-only access for sensitive operations
  - Input validation and sanitization
  - Proper error handling

- Performance:
  - Added database indexes for common queries
  - Optimized report sorting and filtering
  - Efficient notification delivery

Testing:
- Unit tests for content analysis
- Integration tests for report workflows
- Admin interface testing
- Security validation

This implementation helps maintain content quality by:
1. Automating initial content assessment
2. Prioritizing serious reports
3. Streamlining admin workflow
4. Providing clear feedback to users

Breaking Changes: None
Migration Required: No